data.title: WIPO Lex, Member Profile, Armenia
data.meta_description:
WIPO Lex provides free of charge access to legal information on intellectual property (IP) from around the world.
    The WIPO Lex Database is organized into three collections, consisting of IP laws and regulations, WIPO-administered treaties and IPâ€‘related treaties, and IP judgments.
